Package: VietnamWarData
Type: Package
Title: Download Vietnam War Datasets Declassified by NARA
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R:
    person("Gregory L.", "Smith", email = "gregory.l.smith58@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1985-2882"))
Description: Provides functions to download and locally cache Vietnam War
    datasets declassified by the National Archives and Records Administration
    (NARA). Includes ground combat incidents, U.S. casualty records, hamlet
    evaluation surveys, naval gunfire missions, psychological operations
    sorties, base area assessments, and other military datasets spanning
    1963-1974. A combined incident-level dataset joins the major ground combat
    sources into a single analysis-ready file.
